summary: Dual and 2H warriors. Can be married. CBBE, UNPB, HDT. Located in Riften. Nudity. NSFW.
descriptionHtml:
[b][center]

[color=#f4cccc][size=5]Brin and Iwanna Winston[/size][/color][/center][/b][b][center][color=#e06666][size=4](WARNING) These girls are nude until asked to follow. NSFW

[img width=917,height=569]data:image/jpeg;base64,[/img][/size][/color][/center][/b]
[b][center][youtube]AwLPkBa-VHs[/youtube][/center]

Iwanna is a dual wield thieves guild dagger fighter and Brin is a 2H warrior. Both have different perks. Yes, archers too.

[color=#93c47d]Brin and Iwanna are located in Riften, Bee and Barb.[/color]

CBBE, UNPB, and HDT versions available.

They will have no clothes until you ask them to follow and have default vanilla armor and weapons for a more lore friendly experience.

Both are willing to pay you 250 coin each to join up with you. Find it in their inventory after recruiting.

Brin: Sultry voice
Iwanna: Young eager voice

Levels: 5 - 500

One merged .esp file for both girls. Meshes and textures are loose for modifications.

[color=#e69138](Be sure to remove the default hunter bow for each)[/color]

HDT body version requires:

-  HDT Physics Extensions by HydrogenSaysHDT

-  XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended by Groovtama

Be sure to have FNIS as that is important for HDT skeleton.

I use AFT, not tested with EFF. [/b]


Credits and permissions granted where applicable:

CU brows, KS Hairdo's, Multi Colored KS Hairdos, True eyes, The eyes of beauty, Caliente's meshes, Leyenda skin.

Please respect modders and do not upload on other websites. All references and links should be for Nexus only. Feel free to use, modify and enjoy in your own game. Thanks.
